title: GTK 3 PDF Documentation
description:
I wanted to create a more portable version of the GTK+3 documentation, so that people can read it on mobile devices such as tablets or phones. 

This document is for the GTK+ 3 library, version 3.8.2 . The latest versions can be found online at http://developer.gnome.org/gtk3/. If you are looking for the older GTK+ 2 series of libraries, see http://developer.gnome.org/gtk2/.
